---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="Kingdom Messenger Collective — Spirit Media"
	description="The Kingdom Messenger Collective is Spirit Media's flagship formation program — a 3-year journey from heart to movement."
>
	<main id="main-content">

		<!-- HERO -->
		<section class="bg-red-600 text-white py-24 px-4">
			<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
				<p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-red-200 mb-4">Flagship Formation Program</p>
				<h1 class="font-serif text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold leading-tight mb-6">
					Kingdom Messenger Collective
				</h1>
				<p class="text-xl text-red-100 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed mb-8">
					A 3-year formation journey designed to take you from restoration to proclamation —
					heart first, then message, then movement.
				</p>
				<a href="/contact" class="inline-block bg-white text-red-600 font-semibold px-8 py-3 rounded-md hover:bg-red-50 transition-colors">
					Apply for the KMC
				</a>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- WHAT IS THE KMC -->
		<section class="bg-white py-20 px-4">
			<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
				<h2 class="font-serif text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">What Is the Kingdom Messenger Collective?</h2>
				<p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
					The Kingdom Messenger Collective (KMC) is Spirit Media's flagship program for Kingdom
					leaders who sense a calling to carry a message to the world — but haven't yet found the
					clarity, community, or courage to step into it fully.
				</p>
				<p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
					This isn't a course. It's not a mastermind. It's a formation journey — one that begins
					in the heart and ends with a movement.
				</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- THREE-PHASE PATHWAY -->
		<section class="bg-gray-50 py-20 px-4">
			<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
				<h2 class="font-serif text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-12 text-center">The Three-Phase Formation Pathway</h2>
				<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">

					<div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border-t-4 border-red-600">
						<div class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-red-600 mb-2">Phase 1 — Year 1</div>
						<h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Heart</h3>
						<p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
							Before you carry a message, you must know the Messenger who sent it. Phase 1 is about
							deep inner healing, identity formation, and learning to hear the Father's voice.
							We go slow here — because roots determine reach.
						</p>
					</div>

					<div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border-t-4 border-red-600">
						<div class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-red-600 mb-2">Phase 2 — Year 2</div>
						<h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Message</h3>
						<p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
							Every Kingdom Messenger has a specific message for a specific people. In Phase 2,
							we help you clarify what God has uniquely deposited in you — and craft it into a
							message that moves people.
						</p>
					</div>

					<div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border-t-4 border-red-600">
						<div class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-red-600 mb-2">Phase 3 — Year 3</div>
						<h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Movement</h3>
						<p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
							Now it's time to release what's been formed. Phase 3 is about building platforms,
							publishing your message, launching your ministry, and creating generational inheritance.
						</p>
					</div>

				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- THE THREE-YEAR JOURNEY -->
		<section class="bg-white py-20 px-4">
			<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
				<h2 class="font-serif text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">A Three-Year Journey, Not a Three-Day Event</h2>
				<p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
					Real formation takes time. The KMC is built on the conviction that lasting Kingdom impact
					comes from depth, not hype. Each year includes:
				</p>
				<ul class="space-y-4">
					<li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-700">
						<span class="text-red-600 mt-1 font-bold">•</span>
						Monthly live group sessions with Kevin White
					</li>
					<li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-700">
						<span class="text-red-600 mt-1 font-bold">•</span>
						One-on-one mentorship check-ins
					</li>
					<li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-700">
						<span class="text-red-600 mt-1 font-bold">•</span>
						Curated reading and resource lists
					</li>
					<li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-700">
						<span class="text-red-600 mt-1 font-bold">•</span>
						Community with fellow KMC participants
					</li>
					<li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-700">
						<span class="text-red-600 mt-1 font-bold">•</span>
						Milestone projects that advance your calling
					</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- KEVIN WHITE MENTOR SECTION -->
		<section class="bg-gray-50 py-20 px-4">
			<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
				<h2 class="font-serif text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Your Mentor: Kevin White</h2>
				<p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-8">
					Kevin White is the founder of Spirit Media and a seasoned Kingdom voice with over two
					decades of experience in publishing, ministry, and leadership formation. As your primary
					mentor through the KMC, Kevin brings personal attention, prophetic insight, and practical
					wisdom to every participant.
				</p>
				<blockquote class="bg-red-50 border-l-4 border-red-600 p-6 rounded-r-xl">
					<p class="text-gray-700 italic leading-relaxed mb-3">
						"I started the KMC because I was the person who needed it — someone with a message and
						no idea how to steward it. I built the pathway I wish I'd had."
					</p>
					<cite class="text-sm font-semibold text-red-600">— Kevin White</cite>
				</blockquote>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- WHO SHOULD APPLY -->
		<section class="bg-navy-950 text-white py-20 px-4">
			<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
				<h2 class="font-serif text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">Is the KMC Right for You?</h2>
				<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-12">
					<div>
						<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-red-400 mb-4">You're a good fit if...</h3>
						<ul class="space-y-3">
							<li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-300">
								<span class="text-red-400 mt-1">✓</span>
								You sense a calling to carry a specific message
							</li>
							<li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-300">
								<span class="text-red-400 mt-1">✓</span>
								You're serious about long-term formation (not shortcuts)
							</li>
							<li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-300">
								<span class="text-red-400 mt-1">✓</span>
								You value community with other Kingdom leaders
							</li>
							<li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-300">
								<span class="text-red-400 mt-1">✓</span>
								You want publishing and platform support built into your journey
							</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
					<div>
						<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-400 mb-4">This might not be for you if...</h3>
						<ul class="space-y-3">
							<li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-400">
								<span class="mt-1">✗</span>
								You're looking for a quick online course
							</li>
							<li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-400">
								<span class="mt-1">✗</span>
								You want a guaranteed ROI formula
							</li>
							<li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-400">
								<span class="mt-1">✗</span>
								You're not open to inner-healing work
							</li>
							<li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-400">
								<span class="mt-1">✗</span>
								You haven't yet surrendered your calling to God
							</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="text-center">
					<a href="/contact" class="inline-block bg-red-600 text-white font-semibold px-8 py-3 rounded-md hover:bg-red-700 transition-colors">
						Apply for the KMC
					</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

	</main>
</Layout>
